Lighting* & Appliances Program
Instant discounts. Long-term savings. Now even easier.
Saving energy saves you money. So we've partnered with 
					local and online retailers to offer discounts on everything 
					from LED light bulbs to Advanced Power Strips. You'll get 
					instant savings at these
					participating stores. 
					Start shopping and saving now while supplies last.
* Instant discounts for efficient lighting will 
					return in 2016. Check back for a list of partnering 
					retailers. 

Advanced Power Strips+


Advanced Power Strips

Click here for the $10 APS Mail-in Rebate!

Reduce Phantom Power in your house! This is energy that is used by appliances when they are turned off, but still using a small amount of electricity -- and can add up to large impacts. An Advanced Power Strip (APS) is a surge protector that will turn off phantom power when your appliances are plugged in to it, with an energy savings of 85 kWh per year, on average. 


The $10 mail-in rebate applies to these models of APS, which can be purchased on-line. Models on this list use less than 1 watt of power in Stand-by mode and have electrical and coax surge protection where applicable.






		MANUFACTURER 




		ELIGIBLE PRODUCT 




		MODEL # 





