Pool Pumps+


ENERGY STAR® Pool Pump Rebates

Click here for the Mail-in Rebate Application! 


Pool pump energy use can be costly. Pool pump speeds vary based on the pool's operation. Filtration, for example, only requires half the flow rate of running a pool cleaner. Conventional pool pumps, with only one speed, are set to run at the higher speeds required of the pool cleaner and waste energy during filtration operation by running faster than necessary. An ENERGY STAR certified pool pump can run at different speeds and be programmed to match the pool operation with its appropriate pool pump speed. The energy saved is considerable; reducing pump speed by one-half allows the pump to use just one-eighth as much energy. Entergy Solutions offers a $200 rebate for a newly-installed Variable Speed Pool Pump. 


Click here for a $200 Pool Pump Rebate Application Form!


Any residential Entergy Louisiana customer is eligible to receive a rebate for an ENERGY STAR rated pool pump installed in an in-ground pool. 
Contact a Pool Professional to purchase and install an ENERGY STAR Pool Pumps. Apply for the Entergy Solutions Rebate here.




Window A/Cs+


ENERGY STAR® Window Air Conditioner Program
Click here for the Mail-in Rebate Application!


Increase your home's comfort while reducing monthly energy bills by installing a new, high efficiency window air conditioner (A/C). Entergy Solutions provides mail-in rebates for the purchase and installation of energy efficient window units. 





Any residential Entergy Louisiana customer is eligible to receive rebates for ENERGY STAR qualified units purchased from a participating retailer. Each customer can receive rebates for up to four window units. 


Visit any of the Entergy Solutions Retail Partners to purchase a new ENERGY STAR Window Unit, or any retailer who sells ENERGY STAR window units. 


At the time of sale, you will receive a rebate application. Please complete the application and send to Entergy Solutions within 45 days of the purchase. If not available from the retailer, applications can be downloaded here. The installation will then be confirmed and the rebate will be mailed to you within three weeks. 


Rebates are offered on a first-come, first-served basis, and funding is limited. Additional eligible tax credits or rebates may be available. 



All ENERGY STAR Qualified Window units are eligible for a $25 mail-in rebate.




LED Light Bulbs+


Save up to $3 per bulb on LED Light Bulbs

Emitting very little heat and averaging 22 years in lifespan, highly-efficient LED bulbs use as little as six watts of energy -- compared to 40 watts with a traditional incandescent bulb. LED bulbs can be expensive, but for a limited time, you will receive instant savings of up to $8 per bulb when you buy LEDs at participating retailers. 



CFL Bulbs+


Save up to $1.00 per bulb on general-purpose (spiral) CFL Bulbs

Compact fluorescent light bulbs (CFLs) use about 75% less energy than standard incandescent bulbs and last up to 10 times longer -- saving you more than $40 in electricity costs over each CFL bulb's lifetime. Look for in-store discounts on ENERGY STAR spiral CFLs at participating retailers. 					  
					
					




 































































